summary:
- Over 9 years of software development experience with strong technical and functional skills.
- 6 years of experience in the supply chain industry specializing in logistics, distribution and warehouse management systems working with an in-house warehouse management system and Manhattan’s PkMS WMS.
- Technical expertise on the iSeries (AS400) with programming experience in ILE RPG, RPG Free Format, Fully Free Form RPG, CL, CLLE and DB2.
- Worked with IFS, XMLs, FTP, APIs and web services on the iSeries. 
- Certified Dell Boomi Integration Developer.
- Experience with MarkMagic (JMagic) and BarCode400 label designers and ISIS Papyrus document designer tools and Aldon and Turnover change management tools.
- Handled the entire SDLC process from requirement gathering, estimation, development and testing.
- Over 5 years of international experience working in Belgium and Czechia with teams from Belgium, Czechia, Germany, UK and US.
